{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the codebase. Let me analyze what's already implemented vs what the issue requires:\n\n**Already implemented:**\n- `WorkspacePicker` struct with `move_up`/`move_down`/`selected_workspace` (app.rs)\n- `show_workspace_picker` / `cancel_workspace_picker` methods (app.rs)\n- Workspace picker rendering as a popup overlay (detail.rs)\n- Key handling for `j`/`k`, `Enter`, `Esc` on the picker (main.rs)\n- `open_workspace_picker` loads from state and shows picker (main.rs)\n- `start_new_thread` handles the new thread flow (main.rs)\n- Tests for picker navigation, show/cancel\n\n**Missing per the issue description:**\n- `/` to type a new path (with Enter to confirm, Esc to cancel) — currently the picker only supports selecting from existing workspaces, not typing a new path\n- When workspaces list is empty, the `/` flow should still work (currently `open_workspace_picker` returns early if empty)\n\nLet me implement the text-input mode for the workspace picker:"},{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_vrtx_01X1giNREzcS8Bz4rTnD35Yi","name":"Read","input":{"path":"/Users/jmawson/Development/sourcery/ishi/src/api"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22325,"cache_read_input_tokens":57548,"output_tokens":340,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff6f-1764-71ab-959c-1a77c9cfb735"}
