{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01X8HXoRuzUvWPjzeNWAL1nw","content":"[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-92\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Workspace picker modal for starting new Amp threads\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"When starting a new Amp thread from the issue detail view, show a workspace picker overlay:\\\\n\\\\n* Lists previously used workspaces from state file, navigable with j/k\\\\n* `/` to type a new path (with Enter to confirm, Esc to cancel)\\\\n* `Enter` on a listed workspace selects it\\\\n* Selected/entered path is saved to workspace history (moved to top if already present)\\\\n\\\\nRenders as a centered popup over the detail view.\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-92\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-92-workspace-picker-modal-for-starting-new-amp-threads\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:19.120Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T05:35:36.801Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T05:35:36.772Z\\\",\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Done\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"attachments\\\":[],\\\"documents\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"}\"}]","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff6f-1764-71ab-959c-1a77c9cfb735"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"できました！(dekimashita! — Done!) ✅\n\n**Summary of changes for JEM-92:**\n\n- **`WorkspacePicker`** — added `typing: bool` and `input: String` fields, plus `start_typing()`, `cancel_typing()`, and `confirm_typed_path()` methods for the `/` text-input mode\n- **`show_workspace_picker`** — now opens even with an empty workspace list (so users can type a new path via `/`)\n- **Key handling** (main.rs) — when the picker is in typing mode, `Enter` confirms the typed path and starts a new thread, `Esc` cancels back to list mode, `Backspace`/`Char` edit the input; in list mode, `/` enters typing mode\n- **Rendering** (detail.rs) — shows a `/ to type a path` hint at the bottom of the picker, or a text input field with cursor when typing; list highlight is suppressed during typing\n- **9 new tests** covering start/cancel/confirm typing, whitespace handling, empty input, and input accumulation. All 108 tests pass."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":592,"cache_read_input_tokens":95515,"output_tokens":265,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff6f-1764-71ab-959c-1a77c9cfb735"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":151183,"is_error":false,"num_turns":20,"result":"できました！(dekimashita! — Done!) ✅\n\n**Summary of changes for JEM-92:**\n\n- **`WorkspacePicker`** — added `typing: bool` and `input: String` fields, plus `start_typing()`, `cancel_typing()`, and `confirm_typed_path()` methods for the `/` text-input mode\n- **`show_workspace_picker`** — now opens even with an empty workspace list (so users can type a new path via `/`)\n- **Key handling** (main.rs) — when the picker is in typing mode, `Enter` confirms the typed path and starts a new thread, `Esc` cancels back to list mode, `Backspace`/`Char` edit the input; in list mode, `/` enters typing mode\n- **Rendering** (detail.rs) — shows a `/ to type a path` hint at the bottom of the picker, or a text input field with cursor when typing; list highlight is suppressed during typing\n- **9 new tests** covering start/cancel/confirm typing, whitespace handling, empty input, and input accumulation. All 108 tests pass.","session_id":"T-019cff6f-1764-71ab-959c-1a77c9cfb735"}
